/ Rendering errors requires an `obj` and also a `name` - but you can pass in full error_messages instead
- error_messages ||= obj.errors.full_messages

.alert.alert-danger
  %h4
    #{ pluralize(error_messages.count, "error") } prevented this #{name} from being saved:
  %ul
    - error_messages.each do |message|
      %li
        = message
